      "target": {
        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(memory): export LanceDB artifacts for wiki bridge",
        "body": "## Summary\n- add shared workspace public artifact listing for memory bridge consumers\n- make memory-lancedb export a deterministic Markdown bridge artifact for local file-backed dbPath values\n- derive LanceDB bridge artifact agent ids from configured memory workspaces\n- skip LanceDB table Markdown export for URI-backed dbPath values while preserving workspace memory artifacts\n- preserve workspace memory artifacts when memory-lancedb is the active memory plugin\n- preserve only public artifact providers discovered during activate:false loads without retaining prompt, flush, or runtime state\n- render native wiki links without `.md` targets\n\n## Real behavior proof\n- **Behavior addressed**: `memory-wiki` bridge mode should continue exporting/importing public memory artifacts when `memory-lancedb` is the active memory plugin, including the LanceDB memory export and workspace memory Markdown artifacts.\n- **Real setup tested**: Live OpenClaw install on my local workstation, with the equivalent local LanceDB/wiki bridge repair applied. This PR upstreams that repaired behavior into source.\n- **Exact steps or command run after fix**: Ran `openclaw wiki bridge import`, `openclaw wiki status`, and `openclaw wiki lint` against the live OpenClaw setup after the repair.\n- **Evidence after fix**: Copied terminal output from the live setup:\n\n```text\n$ openclaw wiki bridge import\nBridge import synced 35 artifacts across 2 workspaces (0 new, 1 updated, 34 unchanged, 0 removed). Indexes refreshed (2 files).\n\n$ openclaw wiki status\nWiki vault mode: bridge Vault: ready (~/.openclaw/wiki/main) Render mode: native Obsidian CLI: missing Bridge: enabled (35 exported artifacts) Unsafe local: disabled Pages: 101 sources, 1 entities, 9 concepts, 5 syntheses, 10 reports Source provenance: 0 native, 35 bridge, 0 bridge-events, 0 unsafe-local, 66 other\n\n$ openclaw wiki lint\nLinted wiki vault at ~/.openclaw/wiki/main (0 issues, report: ~/.openclaw/wiki/main/reports/lint.md).\n```\n\n- **Observed result after fix**: The bridge import succeeded with 35 artifacts across 2 workspaces, `openclaw wiki status` reported bridge enabled with 35 exported artifacts, and wiki lint reported 0 issues.\n- **Not tested**: I did not replace the live OpenClaw install with this source checkout. The live setup used the equivalent local repair shim; this PR moves that behavior into upstream source. URI-backed `memory-lancedb` behavior and discovery-only memory capability behavior are covered by local regression tests listed below.\n\n## Tests\n- `env OPENCLAW_VITEST_MAX_WORKERS=4 corepack pnpm test -- extensions/memory-lancedb/index.test.ts extensions/memory-wiki/src/markdown.test.ts extensions/memory-wiki/src/bridge.test.ts src/plugins/loader.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.extension-memory.config.ts extensions/memory-lancedb/index.test.ts extensions/memory-wiki/src/markdown.test.ts extensions/memory-wiki/src/bridge.test.ts`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.bundled.config.ts src/plugins/loader.test.ts`\n- `corepack pnpm tsgo:core:test`\n- `corepack pnpm tsgo:extensions:test`",
        "branch": "fix/lancedb-wiki-bridge-artifacts",
